Canonical website:
  https://sites.google.com/site/openimageio/home

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/OpenImageIO/oiio/archive/Release-1.6.1dev.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack OpenImageIO-1.6.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./OpenImageIO-1.6.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/OpenImageIO-1.6.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/OpenImageIO-1.6.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libOpenImageIO1.6-1.6.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libOpenImageIO-devel-1.6.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/python-OpenImageIO-1.6.1-X.tar.xz

